Results.ReviewText: Bought this because I fancied something different. Well I was so impressed by the packaging I had to buy it. It was the best thing I ever did. Will not ngo back to my other brand again. This is my new FAVOURITE
Results.Title: Gold Blend Barista

Results.ReviewText: I bought this recently and won't ever go back to any other coffee has replaced my take out coffee it is the only coffee both my hubby and me will drink it's like having my very own barista in my kitchen love it
Results.Title: Tastest yet

Results.ReviewText: I bought this in Iceland as I was flush and decided to treat myself . I wasn't disappointed with this coffee for it's richness and smoothness which does it's label justice . My money was very very well spent !
Results.Title: A hidden gem

Results.ReviewText: Bought barista style Nescafe gold blend a couple of weeks ago. Tastes like a quality coffee.loved the feeling of sitting down to one of my favourite shows with a cup of barista feeling like I've earned it.
Results.Title: Full of flavour

Results.ReviewText: I am not a great coffee fan, I always have coffee in for friends I have the occasional cup, my friends commented on this so I tried it it is good I have in the past bought gold blend but will now buy this
Results.Title: rich & smooth

Results.ReviewText:
I only had 1 cup of the barista style and unfortunately, its not for me.
I like strong coffee with a kick and do not like the blend.
I will be back to my ORIGINAL NESCAFE because its the taste I prefer.
Results.Title: not for me

Results.ReviewText: I have been using this coffee over the last three months the only way I can sum this up is by saying this is a coffee lovers dream coffee no need for the expensive high street coffee shop for me anymore.
Results.Title: Best Coffee Ever

Results.ReviewText: Coffee shop coffee in your favourite cup. Black or white it fills your senses with the unmistakeable flavour that you expect from Nescafe and the freshness you expect from your own personal barista.
Results.Title: Rich smooth flavour

Results.ReviewText:
I love this coffee! when I wen to the Philippines last July, i bought 7 of this and gave it to my family.  Now, thats sharing the love and quality of the Nescafe Coffee.
I am a solid Nescafe fan!
Results.Title: I am my own Barista!!

Results.ReviewText: My wife originally brought Nescafe Gold Blend Barista style first. I was happy with my previous choice but having tried Barista I am now hooked as well. Great coffee, great taste and ease of use
Results.Title: Coffee at it's best

Results.ReviewText: The new blend Nescafe Gold is Excellent and can compete with the best of its competitors and not only is the taste First Class but the Aroma prepares your taste buds for the first sip !!Bliss...
Results.Title: I love this Coffee!!

Results.ReviewText:
Another great Necafe quality product. 
Smooth but a great all round taste of fresh cofffee.
The nearest thing to ground coffee but all in an instant. A brilliant tasting lift to anyone's day.
Results.Title: Guaranteed Gold Quality

Results.ReviewText: I drink my coffee black and I like the taste of gold blend. It’s not as sharp as Nescafé Original but has a smooth taste. For those that drink their coffee black then I can recommend this one
Results.Title: Fantastic

Results.ReviewText: This is a coffee tasting like a superior coffee.  Equally delightful with or without milk.  Easy to prepare and good value for money considering the price of coffee in cafes and coffee shops.
Results.Title: Unique

Results.ReviewText: Love this product, onced open I store it in the fridge!  I now cannot drink any other instant coffee's - nothing compares.  I love the aroma when you open the lid of the container - heaven!
Results.Title: Tastes like freshly ground coffe - love the aroma!

Results.ReviewText: I bought this a couple of weeks ago for a change I loved it from the first open to the last spoonful the lovely rich coffee smell is still there, the taste is second to none I'm switching!.
Results.Title: Great aroma fabulous taste

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking this brand for a while now,and the taste just roles over your taste buds time after time,every cup is a delight to drink,especially in the morning to start your day.
Results.Title: Taste the fantastic

Results.ReviewText: I have bought this Coffee for some time now. I always used to buy the standard Nescafe Gold Blend but when I tried this (because it was on offer at the time), there was no going back.
Results.Title: Just like the real thing!

Results.ReviewText: I bought this last week, love the taste of strong coffee and this is one that I recommend. I have also got my friends to try it and they are in the same views as me. Well done Nescafe
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText: I decided to try this instead of my usual brand of this style of coffee and I really was impressed.  Great flavour, smooth, no strange after taste.  Will definitely be buying again!
Results.Title: Great taste, loved it!

Results.ReviewText: I love coffee and since trying this I haven't looked back! It's golden :) I'm an instant barista! I have and will continue to recommend this coffee for its taste, value and quality
Results.Title: Bold and Gold

Results.ReviewText: Amazingly smooth and bring that wonderful magic taste to  your taste bud  in an instance...The cost has no bearing when it comes to this exceptional value and aroma into your home
Results.Title: Makes a Perfect waking up day

Results.ReviewText: Was given a tin of this coffee a couple of years ago & I fell in love with it. It has a rich, full, rounded flavour. Cannot tell that it is an 'instant' coffee. Well done Nescafe
Results.Title: Gorgeous

Results.ReviewText: Being a real coffee fan, Nescafe Barista was a real find. It has a lovely rich yet smooth taste. Made with milk or black it is just delicious. A real treat that I enjoy at home.
Results.Title: "Lovely"

Results.ReviewText: Bought this for work and I’ve not looked back since . That I’ve even got my colleagues drinking it too. Great taste and strength like local coffee shop but in my office instead
Results.Title: Great barista coffee

Results.ReviewText: I love the aromatic notes of this coffee. It is strong and subtle and creamy. It is so much better value than going to the coffee shops. This is what gets me up in the morning!
Results.Title: Tastes just like my favourite coffee shop.

Results.ReviewText: all my friends commented on my coffee when i had them around to the house for a catch up and they said they will all be buying nescafe barista as they thought it was fantastic.
Results.Title: lovely taste and aroma

Results.ReviewText: If you like the taste of coffee you would purchase on the go from a high street Coffee shop chain then you must try Gold Blend Barista which tastes far better than them all !!
Results.Title: Barista Style

Results.ReviewText: Always on the look out for a new coffee I stumbled across this Barista version of gold blend and have found my new top taste in an instant. Rich flavour with depth,  I love it
Results.Title: Dark, Deep and Devine

Results.ReviewText: Will now only ever have Nescafé Gold Blend Barista Style coffee. This rich full body instant coffee is the next best thing to freshly ground coffee in a fraction of the time.
Results.Title: Best instant coffee ever
